snippet.title: Luma Island ✧ Wishlist today!
snippet.description:
Wishlist Luma Island on Steam today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2408820?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=firsttrailer_01

Travel to Luma Island to go on an epic adventure by yourself or with your friends and family. Build your dream farm, master professions, collect magical Lumas, find treasures and unravel the mysteries of the island.

Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/kd8TU4AVV2
